Package: TaxaExpect
Title: Estimate Bayesian Priors for Species Occurrence Using GBIF Data
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Kevin", "Lafferty", role = c("aut", "cre"),
    email = "klafferty@usgs.gov")
Description: Generates theta priors (occupancy x detectability) for taxonomic
    assignment from occurrence data (see TaxaFetch). Occurrence data are
    first summarized at the grid level. At this scale, the user is able to apply
    spatial models that generate estimates of theta along with expected error.
    Part of the TaxaID ecosystem.
